  "doc_id": "19170",
  "text": "In evaluating more than 10,000 CF-LVAD recipients in the INTERMACS database, Kirklin and colleagues [CITATION_1] found the following risk factors for increased mortality: elder age, female gender, elevated body mass index, history of stroke, renal dysfunction, right heart dysfunction, surgical complexity, implantation for DT, and INTERMACS profile level 1 or 2 status.",
